genresAdvancedInfo.name: banda militar
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This genre of music is typically associated with military marching bands and is characterized by the use of brass and percussion instruments. Banda Militar music is often played at military ceremonies, parades, and other formal events. The music is typically patriotic and uplifting, and is designed to inspire and motivate soldiers and civilians alike.
